<subSubSection pageId="5" pageNumber="26" type="distribution">
<paragraph pageId="5" pageNumber="26">Distribution.</paragraph>
<paragraph pageId="5" pageNumber="26">The species is known from the Sudan, Ethiopia, Kenya, Tanzania, and Uganda, south to Angola and Malawi and west to southern Senegal.</paragraph>
</subSubSection>
